title: Hitchcock's Vegetarian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Asian, European
description: All-you-can-eat buffet style restaurant, and the first person to book for a particular night gets to choose the food theme. Daily changing menu. Main courses are served from 20:00, and you queue for the buffet. Desserts are then brought out and again you queue.
